# Card Carousel Component

## Overview

A responsive card carousel component based on the provided design.

The component displays cards with images and titles and supports smooth horizontal scrolling with a responsive layout for desktop and mobile devices.

## Features

- Responsive design
- Horizontal card carousel
- Touch-friendly mobile interaction
- Dynamic card rendering from JavaScript data
- Reusable card structure

## Technologies

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Structure

```
project/
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── assets/
    └── images/
```

## Implementation

Cards are generated dynamically from a data array, making the component easy to maintain and extend.

CSS Flexbox is used for the carousel layout and media queries handle different screen sizes.

## How to Run

Open `index.html` in a browser.

No additional dependencies are required.